		Evercore Partners Inc Class A (EVR) Moves Higher on Volume Spike for July 27	

Equities Staff


						Follow					
											|
				Thursday, 27 July 2017 17:18 (EST)










		Market Summary
	
 Follow 





Evercore Partners Inc Class A is a Provides advisory services




Last Price
					$ 77.30				

